Class JSONList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>
        • java.util.ArrayList<Object>
          • com.fortify.util.rest.json.JSONList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Object>, Collection<Object>, List<Object>, RandomAccess

    public class JSONList
extends ArrayList<Object>
    This class represents JSON arrays/lists as a standard Java ArrayList, adding some JSON-related utility methods.
    Author:
    Ruud Senden

    Serialized Form

      • getValues

        public final <R> List<R> getValues(String listValueExpression,
                                   Class<R> listValueType)
        Get a new List with the given value type by evaluating the given SpEL expression on each entry in this JSONList instance. If the given expression evaluates to null for any entry, the entry will be ignored.
        Type Parameters:
        R - Value type for the list to be returned
        Parameters:
        listValueExpression - Expression to be evaluated on each entry in this JSONList
        listValueType - Value type for the list to be returned
        Returns:
        List containing the results of evaluating the given expression on each of the entries in this JSONList

      • filter

        public final JSONList filter(String matchExpression,
                             Object matchValue)
        Filter the current JSONList instance by evaluating the given SpEL expression on each entry, and comparing the evaluation result against the given match value. Each matched entry will be included in the new JSONList instance returned by this method.
        Parameters:
        matchExpression - to be evaluated on each entry in this JSONList
        matchValue - against which to match the outcome of the expression for each entry
        Returns:
        Copy of this JSONList, containing only values for which the given expression result matches the given value

      • mapValue

        public final <M,R> R mapValue(String matchExpression,
                              M matchValue,
                              String returnExpression,
                              Class<R> returnType)
        Find the first entry in this JSONList instance for which the given SpEL match expression matches the given match value, then return the result of evaluating the given SpEL return expression on this entry.
        Type Parameters:
        M - Type of the value to match against
        R - Type of the return value
        Parameters:
        matchExpression - to be evaluated on each entry in this JSONList
        matchValue - against which to match the outcome of the expression for each entry
        returnExpression - to be evaluated as the return value of this method
        returnType - Type of the return value
        Returns:
        Result of evaluating the given returnExpression on the first entry in this JSONList for which the given matchValue matches with the outcome of the given matchExpression

      • find

        public final <R> R find(String matchExpression,
                        Object matchValue,
                        Class<R> type)
        Find the first entry in this JSONList instance for which the given SpEL match expression matches the given match value, and convert that entry to the given value type.
        Type Parameters:
        R - Type of the return value
        Parameters:
        matchExpression - to be evaluated on each entry in this JSONList
        matchValue - against which to match the outcome of the expression for each entry
        type - Type of the return value
        Returns:
        First entry in this JSONList for which the given matchValue matches with the outcome of the given matchExpression, converted to the given type

      • toMap

        public final <K,V> LinkedHashMap<K,V> toMap(String keyExpression,
                                            Class<K> keyType,
                                            String valueExpression,
                                            Class<V> valueType)
        For each entry in this JSONList instance, evaluate the given SpEL key and value expressions, and return a new LinkedHashMap containing the evaluated keys and values.
        Type Parameters:
        K - Key type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        V - Value type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        Parameters:
        keyExpression - Expression used to calculate the map keys
        keyType - Key type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        valueExpression - Expression used to calculate the map values
        valueType - Value type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        Returns:
        LinkedHashMap with keys and values calculated by evaluating the key and value expressions on the entries in this JSONList

      • toJSONMap

        public final <V> JSONMap toJSONMap(String keyExpression,
                                   Class<String> keyType,
                                   String valueExpression,
                                   Class<V> valueType)
        Same as toMap(String, Class, String, Class), but returning a JSONMap instead.
        Type Parameters:
        V - Value type for the JSONMap to be returned
        Parameters:
        keyExpression - Expression used to calculate the map keys
        keyType - must be String.class
        valueExpression - Expression used to calculate the map values
        valueType - Value type for the JSONMap to be returned
        Returns:
        JSONMap with keys and values calculated by evaluating the key and value expressions on the entries in this JSONList

      • toMap

        public final <K,V> LinkedHashMap<K,V> toMap(String keyExpression,
                                            Class<K> keyType,
                                            Class<V> valueType)
        Same as toMap(String, Class, String, Class), but the resulting Map will contain the values from this JSONList instance as-is, without evaluating some SpEL value expression.
        Type Parameters:
        K - Key type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        V - Value type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        Parameters:
        keyExpression - Expression used to calculate the map keys
        keyType - Key type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        valueType - Value type for the LinkedHashMap to be returned
        Returns:
        LinkedHashMap with keys calculated by evaluating the keyExpression on the entries in this JSONList, and the corresponding JSONList entries as values
